{"tid":1051883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學校圖書館翻新　女死者一腳踢","createTime":"2019-03-08T02:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T07:16:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"55abe3f517a5c90473bd57de7e4f98b3fe29f12b","tid":1051883,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:38:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190308/20628409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F20628409&d=%2BySIvleuZbSdMWEfOjMUQugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=2648d6eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F20628409&h=7a89a123\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190308/20628409</a><br />\n<br />\n學校圖書館翻新　女死者一腳踢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190308/large/08la8p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190308%2Flarge%2F08la8p3.jpg&h=0d5f3850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天水圍東華三院李東海小學昨如常上課。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【教師校園墮斃】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天水圍東華三院李東海小學女教師疑不堪工作壓力，前日於校園內跳樓身亡，有傳媒取得東華三院的教師評核表，發現評分項目多達20項，無形中對教師做成極大壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n包辦報價招標購書分箱<br />\n<br />\n東華三院學校的老師每年皆需接受校方評核，據「香港01」取得的東華三院教職員評核指標，發現評核項目有20項，包括守時、勤勉、幹勁及自發性、工作產量、專業知識、專業發展、教學準則、授課效果，甚至對學生關懷及與家長的聯繫等。而每項再細分A至F等級，老師需於所有項目達到B或以上，才能升為助理小學學位教師。<br />\n<br />\n48歲女死者林麗棠生前任圖書館主任，兼教中文科。據了解，該校圖書館早前計劃裝修，林女需「一腳踢」，除負責報價、招標、訂書櫃等，並要計劃重購數萬本書。而購書後的入資料、分箱及圖書分類，亦由林女獨自承擔。有知情人士透露，女死者每周教學超過25教節，工作量繁重。<br />\n<br />\n圖書館主任職能關注組召集人劉寶珊指，圖書館主任需接受專業訓練，是一個專責工作，簽約時並非科目老師，惟如今圖書館主任職位被輕視，校長於教師人手不足時，會要求圖書館主任兼任教職，但同時顧及處理圖書館職務，加重圖書館主任的工作量。<br />\n<br />\n■記者謝志輝  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n造假助友申白居二　東主判社服<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n房委會澄清綠置居　不比公屋細"},{"pid":"e165c8a276b4ec1c1edc3ca3908b9a2ba12222fd","tid":1051883,"uid":6103,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"校長死撚左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條仆街咪龜縮好wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cda88852d24bd3b2476e0a6053d2379c54f7ac9","tid":1051883,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:56:46.000Z","msg":"教學不嬲黑暗<br />\n收益唔少嫁"},{"pid":"b05b66a2fbde7e26625c8410b99a2e00128d34cc","tid":1051883,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"校長出黎跪地道歉未"},{"pid":"0e1f7421e25786449e2db924d73a30f03357b6af","tid":1051883,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T02:58:40.000Z","msg":"又一仆街"},{"pid":"05b469fb34b56c958058912f9f8578a501e18730","tid":1051883,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T03:01:36.000Z","msg":"死者家人咁都忍到唔打㭍個校長"},{"pid":"04355fb6bc4dff7f50eebace672c346b9b59611d","tid":1051883,"uid":72058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f1d1b0a647b8c553123f0606d76d708ca05dd6","tid":1051883,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31c9eb6aafd76a3f918cd04006b1f01495b361f0","tid":1051883,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}